(1, 58, 'Prijevoz učenika', 'prijevoz-ucenika', '<figure><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" title=\"Prijevoz učenika\" src=\"images/Vijesti/prijevoz.jpg\" alt=\"Prijevoz učenika\" />\r\n<figcaption>Prijevoz učenika</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Prodaja učeničkih subvencioniranih karata za autobus počinje 3.9.2018. i traje do 16.9.2018.</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U tom periodu učenici srednjih škola moći će koristiti prijevoz bez karata. Sve informacije oko organizacije autobusnog prijevoza imate na web stranici prijevoznika - <a title=\"Otvori\" href=\"http://www.ap.hr/hr/novosti/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">http://www.ap.hr/hr/novosti/</a> Učenici koji koriste željeznički prijevoz moći će u razdoblju od 03.09.2018. do 16.09.2018. (uključujući i 16.rujan) koristiti prijevoz uz predočenje potvrde koju će dobiti u školi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Učenici koji su upisali prvi razred, trebaju na blagajni željezničkog kolodvora Varaždin, Ivanec ili Ludbreg kupiti novu iskaznicu K-18 po cijeni od 20,00 kuna. Na blagajnu učenik treba donijeti fotografiju veličine 3x3,5 cm uz ovjerenu potvrdu škole o upisu u šk.god. 2018/2019.</p>', 2, 8, '2018-09-19 11:07:01', 714, '', '2018-09-27 05:50:09', 714, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2018-09-19 11:07:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 2, 3, 'prijevoz, AP Varazdin', 'Prodaja učeničkih subvencioniranih karata za autobus počinje 3.9.2018. i traje do 16.9.2018.', 1, 5, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 1, '*', ''),
(3, 65, 'Mary Poppins Returns', 'mary-poppins-returns', '<hr />\r\n<h4><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img src=\"images/1794841_full.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"623\" /></span></h4>\r\n<h4><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The pratically-perfect nanny returns to the big screen to help the next generation of the Banks family.</span></h4>\r\n', '<hr />\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #006e99;\">Synopsis</span></h3>\r\n<p>Mary Poppins is back to help the next generation of the Banks family find the joy and wonder missing in their lives following a personal loss. Emily Blunt stars as the practically-perfect nanny with unique magical skills who can turn any ordinary task into an unforgettable, fantastic adventure and Lin-Manuel Miranda plays her friend Jack, an optimistic street lamplighter who helps bring light--and life--to the streets of London.</p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #006e99;\">Cast</span></h3>\r\n<p>Emily Blunt, Lin-Manuel Miranda, Ben Whishaw, Emily Mortimer, Julie Walters, Colin Firth, Meryl Streep, Pixie Davies, Nathanael Saleh, Joel Dawson, Dick Van Dyke, Angela Lansbury, Jeremy Swift, Kobna Holdbrook-Smith, David Warner, Noma Dumezweni, Tarik Frimpong, Sudha Bhuchar, Steve Nicolson, Christian Dixon, Christopher Godwin, John Dagleish, Karen Dotrice Nalle, Ian Conningham, Chris O\'Dowd, Mark Addy, Edward Hibbert, Christopher Scott, Tara Nicole Hughes, Jim Norton</p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #006e99;\">Directors</span></h3>\r\n<p>Rob Marshall</p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #006e99;\">Producers</span></h3>\r\n<p>John DeLuca, Rob Marshall, Marc Platt, Angus More Gordon, Ben Howarth, Michael Zimmer, Callum McDougall, Jennifer Lane, Caroline Roberts</p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #006e99;\">Writers</span></h3>\r\n<p>David Magee, Rob Marshall, John DeLuca, P.L. Travers</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>{loadmodule mod_banners,Tickets1} </p>\r\n<p> </p>', 1, 16, '2019-12-31 23:00:00', 714, '', '2020-05-10 11:08:13', 714, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2019-12-31 23:00